Title: Barris Ottoman
Body HTML:
An essential complement to a wonderfully livable living room, the Barris ottoman is traditional style with newfound flair. Its indulgently soft and light linen-weave upholstery incorporates a fresh, modern sensibility that feels right at home.

DIMENSIONS

30” W x 23” D x 20” H

Title: Barris Chair
Body HTML:
Barris chair gives stately elegance a sense of newfound flair. Its richly detailed exposed frame and scrolled, rolled arms are hallmarks of traditional style—while the indulgently soft and light linen-weave upholstery is a refreshing twist. The result is a decidedly classic look with the modern comfort and ease you crave.

DIMENSIONS

42” W x 38” D x 38” H

Title: Barris Sofa
Body HTML:
The natural appeal of the Barris sofa is endearing. Toss pillows with brown tones and slate gray are reminiscent of stone. Complemented by solid graphite color pillows, ample scale and deep seating provide plenty of room to take a break and stretch out. You won’t be able to stop rubbing your hand against the soft chenille texture of the tan upholstery.

DIMENSIONS

91” W x 40” D x 40” H
